Configure data source for Windows

1. 	
Open a command prompt.
2. 	
Navigate to the Edge System installation directory: %Program Files%/OSIsoft/EdgeSystem.
3. 	
To configure a data source, run this command.

.\OSIsoft.Data.System.Host.exe Configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSource EndpointUrl=opc.tcp://localhost:5463/SimulationServer

4. 	
Optional: To view configured data sources, run this command.

.\OSIsoft.Data.System.Host.exe Configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSource
